message.text:
Aug.9-10 Australia: Voice Actress KOTONO MITSUISHI comes to Australia! 
8/9-19　オーストラリア：声優・三石琴乃、シドニー上陸！
One of the most prolific and influential voice actresses in Japan,　Kotono Mitsuishi is visiting Sydney! 
Out of her many popular roles, which is your favorite?
Usagi Tsukino in Salior Moon? 
Misato Katsuragi in Neon Genesis Evangelion?
Koume Sawaguchi in Blue Seed?
Mai in Darkside Blues?
Murrue Ramius in Mobile Suit Gundam SEED and Gundam Seed Destiny?
Mink in Dragon Half?
http://www.smash.org.au/guests/kotono-mitsuishi

message.text:
KANJI Quiz!
 Which of the Kanji means "wind"？ Choose the answer!
 1. 幻 2. 風 3. 勝

During the hot summer days in Japan, the sound of the wind-bell makes us feel cool and relax.
http://www.anime-manga.jp/KanjiGame/Ninja/　
「wind」を表す漢字はどれ？暑い夏、涼しい"かぜ"と、"ふう"りんの音色で癒されたいですね～

message.text:
Click! Japan Photo Contest（India / Aug.1st～Aug.29）
FB: https://www.facebook.com/events/291583011021971/?ref=22
The Japan Foundation, New Delhi (JFND) will hold a photo exhibition from 1st of August at the JFND Gallery. The photos capture each applicant's precious moment in Japan, and those exhibited are chosen from very large number of applications which JFND invited.

What was your most special moment in Japan? Join and take a shot! 

ニューデリー：Click! Japan Photo Contest（8月1日～8月29日）
インド在住者を対象に公募した、この1年間に日本で撮った写真の展覧会を行います。インドの方々に、日本はどのように映ったのでしょうか。
WEB: http://www.jfindia.org.in/?event=click-japan-photo-contest-2
